Commander Legends meets D&D in this exciting crossover set! The Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur’s Gate Bundle contains 8 Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur’s Gate Set Boosters—the best boosters to open just for fun—plus exclusive accessories, with 40 basic lands (20 traditional foils and 20 nonfoils), 1 traditional foil promo card with Bundle-exclusive alternate art, 1 oversized Spindown life counter, 1 card storage box, and 2 reference cards.
Each Set Booster contains 15 Magic cards, 1 Art Card, and 1 token, ad card, or card from “The List” (a special card from Magic's history—found in 25% of packs). You’ll find 1–7 cards of rarity Rare or higher, including 1 Foil-Etched card and 1 Traditional Foil, in every pack. A Traditional Foil Land replaces the Land card in 20% of Set Boosters.
• 8 Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur’s Gate MTG Set Boosters
• 1 foil alt-art promo card
• 40 basic land cards (20 foil + 20 nonfoil)
• Spindown life counter + card storage box
